Interface IEvent

All Known Subinterfaces:
IDataSourceSchemaEvent
All Known Implementing Classes:
CardAddedToItemEvent, CardAmendedEvent, CardDeletedFromItemEvent, DataSourceCreatedEvent, DataSourceSchemaAmendedEvent, EntityCreatedEvent, EntityMergedEvent, EntitySupplantedEvent, Event, ItemDeletedEvent, ItemPurgedEvent, LinkAmendedEvent, LinkCreatedEvent, PrimaryPropertiesChangedEvent, SecurityPermissionChangeEvent, SecuritySchemaAmendedEvent, SecuritySchemaCreatedEvent, SetAmendedEvent
public interface IEvent

An event that was generated during command processing, and placed into the event store and onto the event bus.

Since:
2.0
